{"text_id":140532,"tokens":["Distance"," learning"," has"," become"," an"," increasingly"," popular"," option"," in"," classrooms"," across"," the"," country","."," With"," the"," advent"," of"," online"," technology",","," it"," is"," now"," possible"," for"," high"," school"," students"," to"," attend"," classes"," from"," the"," comfort"," of"," their"," own"," homes"," and"," complete"," their"," courses"," without"," ever"," setting"," foot"," in"," an"," actual"," school"," building","."," While"," the"," potential"," benefits"," of"," distance"," learning"," seem"," clear",","," it"," is"," important"," to"," consider"," both"," potential"," drawbacks"," and"," counter","arguments"," before"," deciding"," whether"," or"," not"," this"," should"," be"," offered"," as"," an"," option"," for"," high"," school"," students",".","\n","One"," of"," the"," major"," benefits"," of"," distance"," learning"," is"," that"," it"," allows"," for"," increased"," focus","."," Without"," the"," typical"," classroom"," distractions",","," students"," are"," able"," to"," keep"," their"," minds"," on"," the"," task"," at"," hand"," and"," work"," without"," disruption","."," This"," improved"," focus"," can"," lead"," to"," stronger"," academic"," performance"," and"," better"," grades","."," Additionally",","," distance"," learning"," allows"," for"," more"," flexibility"," when"," it"," comes"," to"," learning"," at"," one","\u2019","s"," own"," pace","."," Students"," have"," the"," freedom"," to"," work"," ahead"," if"," they"," are"," able",","," and"," the"," ability"," to"," go"," back"," and"," review"," if"," they"," need"," further"," assistance","."," This"," improved"," learning"," environment"," can"," lead"," to"," higher"," chances"," of"," graduating"," and"," a"," better"," understanding"," of"," the"," material"," being"," taught",".","\n","However",","," there"," are"," also"," potential"," drawbacks"," to"," offering"," distance"," learning"," as"," an"," option"," in"," high"," school","."," Since"," students"," are"," completing"," their"," courses"," from"," home",","," there"," is"," a"," possibility"," that"," they"," could"," become"," isolated"," from"," the"," school"," community","."," This"," could"," lead"," to"," decreased"," socialization"," and"," a"," lack"," of"," connection"," with"," faculty"," and"," peers",","," both"," of"," which"," are"," important"," to"," a"," successful"," high"," school"," experience","."," Furthermore",","," some"," students"," may"," not"," have"," access"," to"," the"," technology"," needed"," to"," take"," advantage"," of"," distance"," learning","."," This"," could"," create"," an"," unfair"," disadvantage"," for"," those"," students"," and"," limit"," their"," chances"," of"," achieving"," their"," educational"," goals",".","\n","Ultimately",","," I"," believe"," that"," high"," schools"," can"," benefit"," from"," offering"," distance"," learning"," as"," an"," option"," for"," students","."," While"," there"," are"," potential"," drawbacks"," to"," consider",","," the"," potential"," benefits"," outweigh"," them","."," Through"," distance"," learning",","," students"," are"," able"," to"," focus"," without"," distraction"," and"," learn"," at"," their"," own"," pace",","," two"," aspects"," that"," can"," lead"," to"," increased"," engagement"," in"," their"," studies"," and"," greater"," chances"," of"," graduation","."," Therefore",","," I"," believe"," that"," schools"," should"," offer"," distance"," learning"," in"," order"," to"," provide"," all"," students"," with"," the"," best"," path"," toward"," success","."],"sub_source":"outfox","model":"text-davinci-003","label":1}